The best part of the job is
probably thinking like an attacker.

5
00:00:13.652 --> 00:00:18.196
I love that part of seeing how can
I break stuff, seeing a system and

6
00:00:18.196 --> 00:00:20.564
figuring out how can I get into it.

7
