How would I find the credentials?

10
00:00:26.085 --> 00:00:31.118
How would I find the machine
that's useful, and get onto it?

11
00:00:31.118 --> 00:00:35.127
My first day in security,
we were learning a new tool.

12
00:00:35.127 --> 00:00:38.981
The whole organization was in a training,
and they're like,

13
00:00:38.981 --> 00:00:40.664
we're going to throw you in.

14
00:00:40.664 --> 00:00:45.539
It's a one week training to
learn a network analyzer.

15
00:00:45.539 --> 00:00:48.741
